'''Adrar n Sirwa''' (s [[tifinaɣ]]: '''ⴰⴷⵔⴰⵔ ⵏ ⵙⵉⵔⵡⴰ''') d yiwen n [[Adrar|wedrar]] deg [[Ameṛṛuk|Umeṛṛuk]] iy tt-qqnen gar [[Aṭlas ameqran|waṭlas ameqran]] d [[Aṭlas ameẓyan|waṭlas ameẓyan]], Adrar-a iga d isawen (lejyub) [[afarnu|ifarnawen]] deg waddud yeflalen anda id tt-binen [[amenẓaẓ|imenẓaẓen]] d iberkanen, Sirwa iga d [[ifsayen]] n [[afarnu amnissi|ufarnu amnissi]] yettuɣalen ar [[tallit tamyusint]]

== Anezwu ==
[[Ageffur]] id yetteɣlayen deg teɣzi n useggas deg wedrar n Sirwa d ayen yedrusen. Ur izerri ara i 400 mm, acku yezga-d deg yiwet n tama yudsen (iqerben) i [[taneẓruft|tneẓruft]], Maca deg [[isek|isekiwen]] yeflalen yettili-d [[adfel|wedfel]] d [[asemmiṭ|usemmiṭ]] aladɣa deg [[tagrest|tegrest]]

== Imezdaɣ ==
Imezdaɣ n tamiwin-a d [[imaziɣen]] n [[Isusiyen|Sus]] ttidiren s tmekrazt (tafellaḥt) anda teẓẓun [[irden]] d [[timẓin]] d [[azɣer|uzɣer]] ma d tullas zeṭṭent [[taṛakna|tiṛakniwin]] sin akin zznuzayen-tent deg ulzuz n ''Teznaxt'' 

